A: The caption package is currently unsupported by the tagging code, and there is only very light-weight support for configuration of captions. You can try something like this, but be aware that this can change in future.

\DocumentMetadata{tagging=on}
\documentclass{article}
\AddToHook{cmd/@makecaption/before}{\footnotesize}
\NewSocketPlug{caption/label}{boldlabel}
{
\textbf{#1}:~
}
\AssignSocketPlug{caption/label}{boldlabel}
\begin{document}

\begin{figure}
a figure
\caption{a caption}
\end{figure}
\end{document}

