and I want them to work as normal across the page break.

It seems like this should be possible using
\mark_get_marks_for_reinsertion:nNN
, but I don't understand how to make it work.

How can I recover marks from the
\vbox
around the split?

Here's a MWE example showing what I mean and what I want:

\documentclass[twocolumn]{article}

