It's easy to make a single pdf which animates across its pages. pdf frames is way less convenient.

To generate the MWE, run the following codes.

\documentclass[tikz,border=1cm]{standalone}
\begin{document}
\foreach \FRAME in {1,...,120} {
\begin{tikzpicture}
\draw (0,0) -- (1,1);
