. However, when I do that and later render it out as
\usebox{\mybox}
the
xrightmargin
of my listing is not respected. Is there any way to get this to work?

MWE:

\documentclass{beamer}
\usepackage{listings}
\usepackage{color}
\lstset{
language=C,
basicstyle=\footnotesize\ttfamily,
numbers=left,
numberstyle=\footnotesize,
stepnumber=1,
tabsize=2,
